 Ofoegbu Vivian Nkeiruka, wife of renowned On-Air Personality Victor Nwaogu, popularly known as Nkubi, recalls when she went to the market, and how she was mocked and shamed. In a video broadcast on social media, she recounted the experience to her spouse. READ ALSO: “I Am Off The Market”, Says Actor Nkubi; Shares Pre-wedding Photos “I got to the market and someone was now telling me.I know you.I know you from somewhere. I was now waiting to hear the place where he/she knew me. He now said, I can remember you. You got married to that short man with a big head. Like seriously. Nigerians just rest”. See post below:   A post shared by Nwaogu Udochukwu Victor (@nkubi_official)  